Binary/source change: GIF FreeImage dispatch fix
===============================================

Purpose
-------
Make .gif files try Quivi's FreeImage backend before the Windows GDI+ backend.
GDI+ successfully loaded GIFs as static images, preventing the animated GIF
decoder from being used.

Changed file
------------
library.zip

